nodes.text: Nodin-Fe was a male Voss Commando from the planet Voss living during the Galactic War. Around 3640 BBY he was stationed at the Pelath Point outpost in the Pelath-Ri Marches. He felt the influence of the Evuk-Nosk, an ancient Sith starship, and asked a Galactic Republic citizen to find it and bury it before the Gormak could excavate it.
Nodin-Fe is a non-player character from the massively multi-player online role playing game Star Wars: The Old Republic released by BioWare in 2011. He is voiced by Fred Tatasciore.
